data.description: This Stone Oak home is ALL ABOUT LOCATION! From it's cul-de-sac, it is walking distance to all 3 schools, 3 minutes from HEB in one direction, and 3 minutes from Stone Oak Parkway in the other. This 4-bedroom, 2.5 bath, 2-story home has an open floor plan with tons of counter space and storage in the kitchen along with an office/guest bedroom on the first floor. The primary suite is massive and the huge backyard has a private patio and an above ground pool (pool can be removed as well at buyers request). Recent Improvements: New water heater (2022), Deck built (2022), interior painted (2023), Furnace blower motor and control panel replaced (2023).
